@chadk1: You could use the `allowNew` property and custom menu rendering to do something like that:

```tsx
<Typeahead
  allowNew
  options={[...]}
  renderMenu={(results, menuProps) => (
    <Menu {...menuProps}>
      {results.map((r, idx) => {
        if (r.customOption) {
          r.label = 'not_found';
        }

        return (
          <MenuItem key={idx} option={r} position={idx}>
            {r.label}
          </MenuItem>
        );
      })}
    </Menu>
  )}
/>
```

